commit.message:
real.c: Update copyright date.

	* real.c: Update copyright date.
	* emit-rtl.c: Likewise.
	* rtl.h: Likewise.
	* dwarf2out.c: Likewise.
	* config/rs6000/darwin-ldouble.c: Likewise.
	* config/rs6000/rs6000.md: Likewise.

From-SVN: r75742
